et dateValues = {}\\n  let watchItems = {}\\n\\n  /**\\n   *处理 日期 监听\\n   */\\n  function dateWatchHandle(val, oldVal, key, idx) {\\n    dateValues[key] = val\\n    // 由于 dateKeys 只有两个值，所以 idx 只有 0 和 1\\n    // 因为 JS 中 0 = false，1 = true\\n    // 所以 !0 = true 返回 1\\n    // 所以 !1 = false 返回 0\\n    let nextIdx = !idx ? 1 : 0\\n    let nextKey = dateKeys[nextIdx]\\n    dateValues[nextKey] = api.getFormData(nextKey)\\n\\n    let startTimeStr = dateValues[dateKeys[0]]\\n    let endTimeStr = dateValues[dateKeys[1]]\\n\\n    if (startTimeStr) {\\n      let startTime = new Date(startTimeStr)\\n     // if (startTime <= toDay) {\\n    //    vm.$message.error(\'开始时间必须大于今天！\')\\n     //   api.setFormData(dateKeys[0], \'\')\\n     //   startTimeStr = \'\'\\n     // }\\n    }\\n    if (startTimeStr && endTimeStr) {\\n      let startTime = new Date(startTimeStr)\\n      let endTime = new Date(endTimeStr)\\n      // 判断 开始时间 是否大于 结束时间\\n      if (startTime > endTime) {\\n        vm.$message.error(\'开始时间不能大于结束时间！\')\\n        api.setFormData(dateKeys[1], startTimeStr)\\n      } else {\\n        // 计算两个时间间隔多少天\\n        let reduce = Math.ceil((endTime.getTime() - startTime.getTime()) / 86400000)\\n        api.setFormData(leaveDaysKey, reduce + 1)\\n      }\\n    }\\n  }\\n\\n  // 遍历 日期 key 进行监听\\n  dateKeys.forEach((key, idx) => (watchItems[key] = (val, oldVal) => dateWatchHandle(val, oldVal, key, idx)))\\n  api.watch(watchItems)\\n})()\\n\",\"css\":\"/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- */\\n/*      Begin --> Word 风格的表单样式 （请勿修改这块区域内的样式，升级时会直接覆盖这块区域内的所有代码）      */\\n/* ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- */\\n\\n/**\\n * Word 风格的样式增强\\n *\\n *    版本功能：\\n *       1. 给所有加了 .form-grid-word-theme 类名的元素加边框\\n *       2. 去掉 .form-grid-word-theme 里面输入框的边框，使其视觉上铺满父级\\n *       3. 设置 radio 在  .form-grid-word-theme 中的边距\\n *       4. 给所有加了 .form-sub-table-word-theme 的子表设置特定的样式\\n *       5. 当校验失败后 .form-grid-word-theme 下的边框会变为红色，并带有发光式阴影\\n *\\n * @author sunjianlei\\n * @version 4.1\\n */\\n\\n/* \\n    table式风格的表单样式\\n    .el- 开头的都是 element ui 的类名\\n */\\n\\n/* 设置栅格布局的边框，下边距 -1px 可以让边框重合 */\\n.form-grid-word-theme {\\n    border: 1px solid #000;\\n    margin-bottom: -1px !important;\\n}\\n\\n/* 设置每列的右边框 */\\n.form-grid-word-theme > .el-col {\\n    border-right: 1px solid #000;\\n}\\n\\n/* 设置最后一列没有右边框 */\\n.form-grid-word-theme > .el-col:last-child {\\n    border-right: none;\\n}\\n\\n/* 去掉form-item的下边距，让表单更紧凑 */\\n.form-grid-word-theme .el-form-item {\\n    margin-bottom: 0px !important;\\n}\\n\\n.form-grid-word-theme .el-form-item {\\n    position: relative;\\n}\\n\\n.form-grid-word-theme .el-form-item__error {\\n    z-index: 2;\\n    top: calc(100% + 4px);\\n    pointer-events: none;\\n}\\n\\n.form-grid-word-theme .el-form-item:before {\\n    content: \'\';\\n    display: block;\\n    position: absolute;\\n    top: -1px;\\n    left: -1px;\\n    z-index: 3;\\n    width: calc(100% + 2px);\\n    height: calc(100% + 2px);\\n    border: 1px solid transparent;\\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 6px 0px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0);\\n    transition: border-color 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;\\n    pointer-events: none;\\n}\\n\\n/** 设置校验错误时边框为红色 */\\n.form-grid-word-theme .el-form-item.is-error:before {\\n    border-color: red;\\n    box-shadow: 0px 0px 6px 0px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.3);\\n}\\n\\n/* 去掉输入框的边框 */\\n.form-grid-word-theme .el-input__inner,\\n.form-grid-word-theme .el-textarea__inner,\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme .el-input__inner {\\n    border: 0 !important;\\n}\\n\\n/* 设置radio在grid中的边距 */\\n.form-grid-word-theme .form-radio,\\n.form-grid-word-theme .form-checkbox {\\n    margin-left: 12px;\\n}\\n\\n.form-grid-word-theme .form-radio .el-radio,\\n.form-grid-word-theme .form-checkbox .el-checkbox {\\n    margin-right: 8px;\\n}\\n\\n.form-grid-word-theme .form-radio .el-radio:last-child,\\n.form-grid-word-theme .form-checkbox .el-checkbox:last-child {\\n    margin-right: 0;\\n}\\n\\n/* 子表的 Word 风格主题 */\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme .el-table {\\n    border: 1px solid #000;\\n}\\n\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme thead th,\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme tbody td {\\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #000 !important;\\n    border-right: 1px solid #000 !important;\\n}\\n\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme thead th:last-child,\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme tbody td:last-child,\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme thead th:nth-last-child(2) {\\n    border-right: 0 !important;\\n}\\n\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme thead th {\\n    text-align: center;\\n}\\n\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme tbody td {\\n    background-color: #fff !important;\\n}\\n\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme .el-table__body,\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme .el-table__footer,\\n.form-sub-table-word-theme .el-table__header {\\n    table-layout: unset;\\n}\\n\\n/* -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- */\\n/*      End --> Word 风格的表单样式 （请勿修改这块区域内的样式，升级时会直接覆盖这块区域内的所有代码）      */\\n/* -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- */\"},\"onlineForm\":\"oa_leave\",\"allowPrint\":true,\"customRequestURL\":[{\"url\":\"\"}],\"disabledAutoGrid\":true}}', 'oa_leave', NULL, NULL, 1, 1, NULL, 'jeecg', '2019-08-06 18:02:17', 'jeecg', '2019-12-24 10:45:36');
